DESCRIPTION:This event offers standing-room-only access. Limited Accessible
	 Seating on a first come first serve basis. All support acts are subject t
	o change without notice. There is a six ticket limit. Anyone found purchas
	ing above the set ticket limit may have partially or their entire refund c
	ancelled. Please ensure your ticket is pulled up on your phone before arri
	ving to the ticket scanning pedestal for an easy scanning experience. All 
	pedestals are self-scan. There are no refunds or exchanges. There is no re
